    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Expand Kaz's latest adventure!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This is <u>Optional</u> Paid Downloadable Content for <strong>Kaz's Adventure 2: Lost Souls</strong>.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play through 8 new levels!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Adventure through 6 reimagined levels from &quot;World 1&quot; in Kaz's Adventure (2022.) and 2 new bonus  levels using the original games level design process.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Reimagining!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>6 of the 8 levels featured within the DLC have been reimagined from Kaz's Adventure (2022.), using Kaz's Adventure 2: Lost Souls (2024.) new level design elements such as slopes, one way platforms, enemy health bars, lighting and more!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Obtain new Pets and Survival settings!</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Along with new levels this DLC also includes 4 new pets that instantly unlock upon opening the game and 3 new survival mode settings that will randomly get chosen once survival mode is unlocked.</i>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Pets:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Classic Kaz Pet </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Classic Zaz Pet </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Classic Bob Pet</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic Cloaked Pet</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Survival Settings:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wild Jungle - Survival Setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fields - Survival Setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stone Temple - Survival Setting</p></li></ul>",
